{"_createdAt":"2025-07-01T03:13:15Z","_id":"16bb936f-04e2-44f6-aaa1-9c7024cfbb83","_rev":"Q1s5eURCW2SXWBHYdqf4da","_system":{"base":{"id":"16bb936f-04e2-44f6-aaa1-9c7024cfbb83","rev":"Bw51ceYcMLhBznFqd8TV5k"}},"_type":"post","_updatedAt":"2025-07-01T12:30:40Z","body":[{"_key":"af9e6d49699d","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"a57d1380bfee","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"最近の海況情報"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"a9f09bacf71a","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"844b7a257758","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"49939d0d14f8","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0c86479acad7","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"最近は本当に暑いですね！連日の猛暑で、陸上にいるだけで汗だくになってしまいます。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"8d7fa71efaca","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ee7b5741128f","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"243ae88db87d","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e1f4af5bac30","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"そんな中、三浦海の学校の海況をお知らせします。プールの水温は30度まで上がっていて、まるでお風呂のような暖かさです。一方、海の水温は24度と、プールより少し涼しくて気持ちいい温度になっています。透明度も5〜6メートルと良好で、海の中の世界がはっきりと見えるコンディションが続いています。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"e3a489d1c84c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"d774a5ca01c9","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"e7232ef39bb6","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"07feadc1695a","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"ここ最近は海況がとても良好で、ダイビングには絶好の日が続いています。暑い夏には、やっぱり海が一番ですね！"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"4b4d13dde52f","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c9744bb11d8e","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"7ed18759d22e","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"1153e3a30c93","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"ブログとホームページを一新しました"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"4aaccb1eb5d1","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"5c168566856d","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"b17ef06b2e89","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"2611795a4768","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"さて、本題ですが、この度、三浦海の学校のブログとホームページを全面的に新しくしました！"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"51de3b9ca090","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"558d58b7d757","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"153b84740219","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"76d05abda4fa","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"今まではWordPressというシステムを使っていたのですが、これがなかなか大変で...。例えるなら、古いガラケーでLINEをしようとするような感じでしょうか。機能はあるんだけど、使うのにとても時間がかかって、思うようにいかないことが多かったんです。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"18efcf11532b","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"9e95681b7363","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"9159df87a9bc","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"1ad16085c466","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"WordPressの何が大変だったのか"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"45263f18259b","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"71dfc7632135","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"8b0b5adfeb44","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"667ab9192fbc","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"ログインが面倒すぎる"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"46b3d153fd0a","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e9286fc12ead","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"0fb36074360a","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"bbfd602adabf","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"WordPressでブログを更新するには、毎回管理画面にログインしなければなりません。これが本当に面倒で、例えるなら「家の鍵を開けるのに、毎回5つの鍵を順番に開けなければならない」ような感じでした。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"cc7c201b0d76","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"5daa34d64de7","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"72b1bac633fe","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"06a0271878e7","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"海から上がって、お客様の楽しかった体験をすぐにブログで紹介したいのに、ログインに時間がかかって、その間に「あとでやろう」となってしまうことがよくありました。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"2ffaae9545e5","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"4854eec95691","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"068a6bd5c260","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"8d8f1b087cfd","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"更新作業が複雑"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"abde2369c5bd","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"bc71672fb7e3","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"df3ac7560c52","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ac8e91eb8b58","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"記事を書くのも一苦労でした。例えるなら、「お手紙を書くのに、まず封筒を作って、便箋を作って、ペンを作ってから文字を書く」ような感じです。写真を1枚載せるだけでも、いくつものステップを踏まなければならず、時間がかかりすぎていました。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"307e2c4101de","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7cf87e5503c5","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"0e5ae8041196","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e602a7b1de41","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"海でのダイビングは楽しいのに、その報告をブログに書くのが大変すぎて、だんだん更新が億劫になってしまっていたんです。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"c70c68223465","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"6e6f71b27c24","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"beb3963543a7","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"90fc7ae67db2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"スマホで見にくい"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"eaab67b57ac3","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"525dfd55216b","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"26a81f98fd34","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e1635346c17f","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"最近はほとんどの方がスマートフォンでウェブサイトを見ますよね。でも、古いWordPressのテーマでは、スマホで見たときに文字が小さすぎたり、写真がうまく表示されなかったりしていました。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"a4a5384f09c9","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0bf326cf60a7","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"6bd0f2cd25e6","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0e21f63be51f","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"これは例えるなら、「新聞をそのまま縮小コピーして読む」ような感じで、とても読みにくかったんです。特に海の美しい写真をお見せしたいのに、スマホではその魅力が伝わりにくい状態でした。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"aab672c581b8","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"3e7be839d5c4","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"d6a21cc8e714","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"63597f24f9d5","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Vibe Codingって何？"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"57b5779711d5","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"3a701164aecf","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"57382a50dd4e","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"4985373e44a0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"そこで今回採用したのが「Vibe Coding」という新しい技術です。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"1ba523dfd1e6","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7aaa4c22d78b","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"67e8c01e0604","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"393c305acd68","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"AIが手伝ってくれる"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"ed39af22d877","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"6df9ae76d92c","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"e9bf7e4eddac","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"dfe54f10f3b6","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Vibe Codingの一番すごいところは、AI（人工知能）が手伝ってくれることです。例えるなら、「とても優秀な秘書さんが24時間365日お手伝いしてくれる」ような感じです。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"b84e7eea2d81","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"63087eafd098","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"b5125025ef01","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ed91cfad41a8","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"「海の写真をきれいに見せたい」と思うだけで、AIが自動的に最適なレイアウトを作ってくれます。まるで魔法みたいですよね！"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"09ea74c91671","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"048a8ff4f4b1","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"abb2b64d9c23","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0353a25410b4","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"更新がとても簡単"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"e398a8ab0544","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ff3d08b879ad","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"29a8cca35e43","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"b3892b54d4a8","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"新しいシステムでは、ブログの更新がとても簡単になりました。例えるなら、「LINEでメッセージを送る」ような感覚で、海での出来事をすぐに皆さんにお伝えできるようになりました。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"793316b96fab","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"5e3afcc6c8b0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"77d3da20ff27","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"923c360a22f2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"ダイビング中に見つけた珍しい魚の写真も、海から上がってすぐに「今日はこんな魚に会えました！」とサクッと投稿できるんです。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"76f11f598dec","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7d6e0872616b","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"0495a96c1d53","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"96e7edcd5aa1","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"どんなデバイスでも見やすい"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"3293aa5bf0ee","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"61cd8f751c0a","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"257cbd45775c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"96c998789285","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"新しいサイトは、パソコンでもスマートフォンでもタブレットでも、どの機械で見ても自動的にきれいに表示されます。例えるなら、「どんなサイズの額縁に入れても、写真が自動的にぴったり収まる」ような感じです。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"01a613bfc84c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0ced0f5db250","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"0016bb5790d4","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ae97057e8dc7","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"スマホで見ても海の写真の美しさがしっかり伝わるようになりました！"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"65fafd95a413","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"834018a679fc","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"5ee201a70c48","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"b4463fed5b91","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"具体的に何が良くなったの？"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"b2b567ccc260","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"799d2ae34e28","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"4f2193a440e3","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c0253009bdbe","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"写真がもっときれいに"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"eaf78b613477","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0a3b0159ba9d","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"5bc50d2b0058","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"8b95a6c104ae","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"海の中で撮った写真や、船上からの景色の写真が、以前よりもずっときれいに表示されるようになりました。例えるなら、「普通のテレビから4Kテレビに変えた」ような感じで、色鮮やかさが全然違います。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"0a32c2f4906e","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"999c25f5b6a2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"0c7611546c16","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"57c086266956","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"読み込みが速い"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"3b0b9a9c52d8","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"8cb26ec8df18","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"53a2150cb859","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"9cbc515000d6","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"ページを開いたときの表示速度も、以前の約3倍速くなりました。例えるなら、「エレベーターの扉が開くのを待つ時間」くらいで、すぐにページが表示されます。イライラして待つ時間がほとんどなくなりました。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"f9dcdf6ca77d","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"1fd2515cd7a7","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"0b812d0c386e","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"d38a07b9d491","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"情報が見つけやすい"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"b1b658b4ad48","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"69f15cbf23b3","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"bdcbef8e1baa","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"24ab5c06f8c1","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"欲しい情報がすぐに見つかるように、メニューの配置も工夫しました。例えるなら、「よく使うものを手の届く場所に置いた」ような感じで、ダイビングコースの情報や料金表なども、迷わずにたどり着けるようになっています。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"4cb